== 重製版 ==
提升了畫質及改善了遊戲系統的重製版（''Redux''）使用{{le|4A引擎|4A Engine}}，已分別於2014年8月26日於北美及2014年8月29日於歐洲發售，登錄[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/24/metro-redux-release-date-announced|title=Metro Metro: Redux release date announced|publisher=ign.com|date=2014-06-24|accessdate=2014-08-07|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627054224/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/24/metro-redux-release-date-announced|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年2月，重製版被進一步移植到 [[Nintendo_Switch|Nintendo Switch]] 發售，並獲得良好評價。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Metro 2033 And Last Light Switch Ports Are Stunning, Both Out Now|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/metro-2033-and-last-light-switch-ports-are-stunnin/1100-6474220/|accessdate=2020-04-17|work=GameSpot|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228222742/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/metro-2033-and-last-light-switch-ports-are-stunnin/1100-6474220/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

